    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional choice for a daily driver. The exterior shows visible signs of age, including several noticeable scratches on the side panels and a few small dings on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some fading and minor staining from regular use. All major mechanical systems are operational, though the engine would benefit from a routine tune-up soon. It's a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
