    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver or long-distance travel. While the exterior and interior are clean and well-kept, you may find minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, such as small surface scratches or slight interior aging. Overall, it is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
